pants when one of them is fired?

730
01:52:56.151 --> 01:52:58.489
Take a short break. please.

731
01:53:03.981 --> 01:53:06.190
With every step you take.

732
01:53:06.190 --> 01:53:09.689
I can tell you how direct your economic
